page.title: 07CROPS
page.content: The most usual crops you find in fields are{BARLEY and WHEAT}Sometimes they grow{OIL SEED RAPE}for the cattle We only saw {OIL SEED RAPE}on the edges of the fields and we thought it was last years crop. We saw a lot of wild oats.We saw lots of grasses in the fields with the wheat and barley such as:{COCKSFOOT, {CRESTED DOGSTAIL,SLENDER FOX TAIL, {TIMOTHY,and CRESTED HAIR GRASS.}We saw a lot of flowers growing with the crops like {POPPIES,BUTTERCUPS,CLOVER, and sometimes {JACOBS LADDER}When crops are mixed with grasses,it is probably for {HAY and SILAGE.}
